HOUDINI MENUS
=============

   Major        UP, DOWN                MOVES topic selector
   =====        RIGHT (or ENTER)        DISPLAYS topic details
                LEFT (or ESC)           RETURNS to previous location
                L                       LOOKUP in glossary for related details
                S                       SEARCHES text using auto-synonyms

   Useful       Ctrl-Home               RETURNS to MAIN screen
   ======       M or F6                 MARKS a topic for future reference
                P                       PRINTS a topic
                Q, X, or Alt-X          QUITS the program

   Minor        G                       GOTO a file (such as SEARCH.TXT)
   =====        D                       DOS/PROGRAM call
                E                       EDITOR loaded with displayed file
                V                       VIEW sequence of selected topics

                H                       Lists files with jumps TO current topic
                C                       COLOR settings
                HOME, End, PgUp, PgDn   CHANGES page displayed
                Alt-F6 / Alt-F8         Clears BOOKMARK.TXT / CLIP.TXT files

